 Description:
 This P-1 Line Item is part of the Military Intelligence Program (MIP). It includes purchases that provide for Intelligence, Surveillance, and Reconnaissance (ISR) in support of irregular warfare operations. This
 line funds Special Operations-peculiar (SO-p) modifications and rapid fielding to crewed ISR aircraft. Primary mission emphasis is on signals intelligence, imagery, target acquisition, threat warning, threat
