 Description:
 The Non-Standard Aviation (NSAv) Line Item provides funding to purchase, modify, equip, and rapidly field Special Operations Forces (SOF) NSAv and C-27J aircraft. This line item also funds simulator block
 upgrades (SBUD) to NSAv training devices to address obsolescence, concurrency, and fidelity training issues. Procurement and low cost modifications of NSAv assets support worldwide SOF mobility and
 priority partner nation training. The NSAv program provides SOF with mobility capabilities in austere environments, as well as humanitarian assistance evolutions such as casualty and non-combatant evacuation
 operations.




