 fatigue and corrosion issues. Funds Government Furnished Equipment (GFE)/Special Operations-peculiar mission kits, block modifications, production engineering, publications, and program management.
 Funds modifications to address emerging threats, safety concerns, reliability and maintainability issues, and improved capabilities.

