 This P-1 Line Item provides for the procurement, rapid fielding, and associated costs of specialized equipment in the areas of aircraft support; military construction (MILCON) collateral equipment; Command,
 Control, Communications, and Computer Information and Automated Systems (C4IAS); Tactical Local Area Network (TACLAN); Special Access Program Network (SAPNET); joint operational stocks (JOS); base
