Justification:
The FY2027 budget requests Advance Procurement for long lead materials to support Airframe and Engine long-lead parts necessary to protect delivery schedules. Full funding for long lead end items requesting
advance procurement is included in the budget submission.

FY2027 budget exhibits include funding to support the procurement of Other GFE - APG-85 radar to replace the APG-81 radar in United States versions of F-35 aircraft. Due to extra-long lead times, the APG-85
requires advance procurement for long-lead materials and radar completion for on-time install into the completed aircraft. The first year of APG-85 adv procurement procures radar long-lead materials and the
second year of AP continues material buys, to manufacture and deliver the APG-85 for integration onto US-only aircraft.




